The Weeknd’s seductive vocals are already mesmerizing, but when Jennie and Lily-Rose jump in, it’s pure vocal perfection. Jennie’s sultry tone adds fierce contrast, while Lily-Rose’s whispery delivery brings haunting vulnerability. Together, their voices create a hypnotic mix of desire, temptation, and heartbreak. Masterpiece!

The lyrics express the singer's desire for a relaxed, no-strings-attached encounter. They're not in pursuit of a lasting relationship or aiming to be someone's special partner. Instead, they simply want to share time with the person as a companion without any romantic commitments. It's a straightforward message about seeking a temporary connection without getting emotionally entangled.
